    • Method Detail

      • createOutputSetForTaskAndEdges

        public static java.util.List<OutputSet> createOutputSetForTaskAndEdges(Node task,
                                                       java.util.List<Edge> edges)
        Creates an Output Set for the given Node (task) and the given Edges (edges). The edges should at least contain all outgoing associations of the task, but can contain more edges.
        Parameters:
        task - The task which has an output set
        edges - The list of all edges that are part of the fragment the task belongs to (the list has to contain at least all the outgoing associations of the task)
        Returns:
        The newly created OutputSets or null if no outgoing (DataFlow)-Associations were found.
